Greg Wise https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greg_Wise 0 Matthew Gregory Wise (born 15 May 1966) is an English actor and producer. He has appeared in many British television works, as well as several feature films (notably the role of John Willoughby in Sense and Sensibility).
